n.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/59.mp3","time_start":166.04,"time_end":168.09},{"position":60,"content":"And presumably the day and time are flexible.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/60.mp3","time_start":168.25,"time_end":172.07},{"position":61,"content":"Oh yes. Just say when would suit you best, and we'll let Mr Selsbury know.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/61.mp3","time_start":172.18,"time_end":177.52},{"position":62,"content":"Good.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/62.mp3","time_start":178.03,"time_end":178.54},{"position":63,"content":"The volunteers group also organises monthly social events,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/63.mp3","time_start":179.95,"time_end":184.52},{"position":64,"content":"which is a great way to meet other people, of course.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/64.mp3","time_start":184.52,"time_end":187.64},{"position":65,"content":"So next month, on the 19th of October,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/65.mp3","time_start":188.64,"time_end":192.89},{"position":66,"content":"we're holding a quiz,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/66.mp3","time_start":192.89,"time_end":194.76},{"position":67,"content":"a couple of residents are great at planning unusual ones,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/67.mp3","time_start":194.95,"time_end":198.96},{"position":68,"content":"and we always fill the village hall.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/68.mp3","time_start":198.96,"time_end":201.24},{"position":69,"content":"That sounds like fun.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/69.mp3","time_start":201.34,"time_end":203.03},{"position":70,"content":"Can I do anything to help?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/70.mp3","time_start":203.24,"time_end":205.1},{"position":71,"content":"Well, because of the number of people,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/71.mp3","time_start":205.29,"time_end":208.12},{"position":72,"content":"we need plenty of refreshments for halfway through.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/72.mp3","time_start":208.12,"time_end":211.97},{"position":73,"content":"So, if you could provide any, we'd be grateful.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/73.mp3","time_start":212.1,"time_end":215.67},{"position":74,"content":"I'm sure I could.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/74.mp3","time_start":216.03,"time_end":217.21},{"position":75,"content":"I'll think about what to make, and let you know.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/75.mp3","time_start":217.32,"time_end":220.28},{"position":76,"content":"Thank you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/76.mp3","time_start":220.28,"time_end":221.31},{"position":77,"content":"Then on November the 18th,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/77.mp3","time_start":221.53,"time_end":224.17},{"position":78,"content":"we're holding a dance, also in the village hall.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/78.mp3","time_start":224.17,"time_end":228.36},{"position":79,"content":"We've booked a band that specialises in music of the 1930s,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/79.mp3","time_start":228.53,"time_end":233.75},{"position":80,"content":"they've been before, and we've had a lot of requests to bring them back.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/80.mp3","time_start":233.9,"time_end":238.54},{"position":81,"content":"I'm not really a dancer, but I'd like to do something to help.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/81.mp3","time_start":238.89,"time_end":243.2},{"position":82,"content":"Well, we sell tickets in advance,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/82.mp3","time_start":243.43,"time_end":246.85},{"position":83,"content":"and having an extra person to check them at the door, as people arrive, would be good,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/83.mp3","time_start":246.94,"time_end":252.6},{"position":84,"content":"it can be quite a bottleneck if everyone arrives at once!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/84.mp3","time_start":252.75,"time_end":256.32},{"position":85,"content":"OK, I'm happy with that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/85.mp3","time_start":256.32,"time_end":258.57},{"position":86,"content":"Oh, we're also arranging a New Year's Eve party.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/86.mp3","time_start":258.8,"time_end":262.63},{"position":87,"content":"We're expecting that to be a really big event,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/87.mp3","time_start":262.63,"time_end":265.9},{"position":88,"content":"so instead of the village hall, it'll be held in the Mountfort Hotel.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/88.mp3","time_start":265.9,"time_end":270.77},{"position":89,"content":"The...?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/89.mp3","time_start":271.14,"time_end":271.98},{"position":90,"content":"Mountfort.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/90.mp3","time_start":271.98,"time_end":273.15},{"position":91,"content":"Mountfort Hotel.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/91.mp3","time_start":273.15,"time_end":282.28},{"position":92,"content":"It isn't in Southoe itself, but it's only a couple of miles away.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/92.mp3","time_start":282.6,"time_end":287.45},{"position":93,"content":"The hotel will be providing dinner and we've booked a band.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/93.mp3","time_start":287.58,"time_end":291.94},{"position":94,"content":"The one thing we haven't got yet is a poster.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/94.mp3","time_start":291.94,"time_end":295.95},{"position":95,"content":"That isn't something you could do, by any chance, is it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/95.mp3","time_start":296.09,"time_end":299.32},{"position":96,"content":"Well actually, yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/96.mp3","time_start":299.67,"time_end":301.53},{"position":97,"content":"Before I retired I was a graphic designer, so that's right up my street.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/97.mp3","time_start":301.65,"time_end":306.79},{"position":98,"content":"Oh perfect!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/98.mp3","time_start":306.79,"time_end":308.28},{"position":99,"content":"I'll give you the details,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/99.mp3","time_start":308.28,"time_end":310.46},{"position":100,"content":"and then perhaps you could send me a draft...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/100.mp3","time_start":310.46,"time_end":313.07},{"position":101,"content":"Of course.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-17-test-2-section-1-2022-12-22-23-05-46/101.mp3","time_start":313.1,"time_end":314.13}]}